<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
OS_printf calls OS_DEBUG in the uninitialized-state branch. If OS_DEBUG is implemented by calling OS_printf (a common pattern for a debug logging macro) then the call chain is OS_printf -> OS_DEBUG -> OS_printf, producing indirect recursion and thus violating MISRA C 2023 Rule 17.2. Similarly, if the BUGCHECK_VOID macro expands to call OS_printf when its condition fails, a call with a failing check would cause OS_printf -> BUGCHECK_VOID -> OS_printf (indirect recursion).
</scenario>
